BronKerboschMaximalCliqueFinder
public interface MaximalCliqueFinder<V extends Vertex>

An interface for algorithms that find all maximal cliques in a graph. A maximal clique, sometimes called inclusion-maximal, is a clique that is not included in a larger clique.

Version:
Dec 30, 2009
